These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: trance, punk, jazz, rock, classical, gospel
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, ferret, fish, turtle, chinchilla
 1. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5
 3. the fan of classical is not the owner of the turtle##6
 4. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5
 5. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 6. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
 7. the owner of the turtle is not the fan of punk##6
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of trance is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the fan of rock##7
10. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
12. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
13. the owner of the dog is the fan of trance##1
14. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
15. the fan of gospel is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | trance | jazz   | gospel     | punk    | classical   |
| Pet           | turtle | dog   | chinchilla | fish | ferret | goat |

