.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, epic, sports, zombie, mystery, romance
6 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, turtle, bird, cat, rabbit
 1. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 7. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 8. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not the owner of the cat##6
10. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the bird##7
11. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person watching mystery movies##5
12. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
14. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
15. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
16. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
17. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the person watching mystery movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | romance | zombie | mystery     | sports      | action |
| Pet           | ferret         | turtle        | cat   | bird | rat | rabbit    |

