.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, fanta, juice, 7up, milk
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, snowboarding, volleyball, climbing, weightlifting, golf
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person drinking juice##6
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking coffee##7
11. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
13. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
14. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | 7up        | juice | milk    | iced-tea    | fanta | coffee |
| Sport      | snowboarding | weightlifting  | golf | climbing | biathlon | volleyball      |

