 9. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
12. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the owner of the hamster and the person driving the subway##7
13. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | cat   | mouse | frog      | chinchilla | turtle  | hamster   |
| Transport   | car | van  | subway | bike   | scooter | airplane |

