.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: skydiving, board-games, chess, fishing, rock-climbing, baking
The people have 6 different jobs:  videographer, pilot, musician, bartender, firefighter, writer
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the bartender and the pilot##7
 5. the writer is on the left or right of the musician##3
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is the firefighter##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
 8. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 9. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
10. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the writer##5
11. the writer is on the right of the musician##1
12. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is chess##7
14. the pilot is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
15. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | chess         | fishing | board-games | skydiving   | baking | rock-climbing  |
| Job     | firefighter | bartender  | musician  | writer | pilot  | videographer |

 